现。他指出，受到通货膨胀、利率上升以及经济增长放缓和地缘政治不确定性的影响，美国银行业将继续面临显著的下行风险，美国银行信贷质量和盈利能力可能会被削弱，并进一步导致贷款收紧、融资流动性受到限制。美国联邦储蓄保险公司将对银行业状况进行持续密切关注。美国联邦储蓄保险公司：一季度美银行存款总额降幅刷新历史纪录"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a9fa8de3913c9c83a7410ff95f8d3b59_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604379959"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4It8eQjqbEgbstEAMaCDk2NTg2ODY5IKSP5aMGMAQ4bEAvcgk2MDQzNzk5NTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "48_1685772409.022069", "card_id": "Q_599287344", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 60}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "化学有何种特殊性使其脱离物理成为一门独立学科，而不是和力学、热学、电学等并列？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-5be40bd08e01d4083decb6168faf7d56_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/599287344"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8It8eQjqbEgbstEAMaCDk1NDU1NTkxINP006IGMAM4ywFAMHIJNTk5Mjg3MzQ0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "49_1685772409.0226545", "card_id": "Q_602723066", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 44}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "焦虑型遇上半回避型，有没有好的办法呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "我们宿舍只相距 30 米，但她甚至不想天天见面，而我见不到她又很焦虑。。 但我一个大男人又不好天天腆着脸皮跟她撒娇要陪伴，更何况很多次我都腆着脸皮约她了，她会拒绝，理由是累啊，明天不是又见面了今天想自己玩会啊什么的。。 我好难受呀，大家能不能支个招呢～"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-e02d50b1b665b38df00ddfc535f004ee_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www